[src:south-australian-national-football-league/1871-south-australian-football-season] It was resolved that as the football season was closing, and there being a Cricket Club called the Young Australians, the name be changed to the Union Cricket and Football Club.
[src:south-australian-national-football-league/1871-south-australian-football-season] The following officers were elected:— F.
